\section{Computation of some observables including squark FV.}
The flavor violating parameters, generated from the RGE runing,  enter at one loop in the computation of the physical observables.  Numerically,  the results
have been obtained using the code 
{\tt FeynHiggs}~\cite{feynhiggs}, which contains the complete set of one-loop corrections from (flavor
violating) squark and slepton contributions as given is ref.~\cite{arana}.

